<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041294-0048 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 031429 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 12, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
