in a 92-40 victory over Loara. 
</P>
<P>
 * Sean Morrison, El Dorado, had 30 kills in a five-game victory over Valencia. 
</P>
<P>
 * Craig Wilson, Marina, had 10 RBIs in leading the Vikings to the championship 
of the Dole Big West tournament. 
