firing at him as they drove down Garden Grove Boulevard. The other car 
disappeared, fleeing in a different direction. 
</P>
<P>
 Eventually, according to Lt. John Woods, a spokesman for the Garden Grove 
Police Department, the car Zachman was following hit a retaining wall near 
Memory Lane and Flower Street in Santa Ana, where its three occupants were 
arrested by Santa Ana police. 
</P>
<P>
 The photographer was not injured. 
</P>
<P>
 Police are searching for the occupants of the other car involved in the 
gunfight. They believe that the incident was gang-related. 
