</P>
<P>
 "He was kind and generous and would help anyone who needed help," said Raeann 
Mercado, his sister-in-law. 
</P>
<P>
 Police said Jose Mercado, 37, a construction worker, was driving on Parthenia 
Street near Columbus Avenue about 2 a.m. Sunday in North Hills when he spotted 
a friend, Sylvia Gamez, being beaten by another man. 
</P>
