</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041294-0237 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 031618 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 12, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
